# Shields

A shield is more than defensive equipment—it's a tactical choice that defines your combat approach. Trading offense for defense, a shield grants substantial Guard bonuses at the cost of your off-hand. The difference between a medium weapon wielded two-handed and that same weapon paired with a shield often means surviving long enough to win rather than delivering maximum damage quickly.

